{"tid":1626651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消防處副處長發內部訊息　籲屬員盡力拯救人命","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T01:19:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ff012271da5c5d555b55e5db908fddae32cb9e1d","tid":1626651,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:18:42.000Z","msg":"深水埗一名男子昨晚在消防車輛前被襲，消防處副處長梁偉雄發出緊急內部訊息，呼籲屬員盡力拯救人命。<br />\n<br />\n梁偉雄表示，近日香港多區發生各類違法事件，消防處人員曾被指控縱容暴徒縱火，甚至對一名被多人圍攻的人見死不救，處方管理層深知屬員的法定職責、裝備、訓練及經驗都不可以應付這些暴徒，但會在拯救生命的大前提下，呼籲屬員盡力拯救人命，又說儘管面對暴力，屬員亦應挺身而出，無畏無懼拯救生命。<br />\n<br />\n梁偉雄又說，處方會總結經驗，加強應對有關事故的指引。"},{"pid":"1d3270e0405bfe2f02a7d460c4d3fe97b811e1e7","tid":1626651,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484475-20191005.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484475-20191005.htm&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=94f1db48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484475-20191005.htm&h=351f4caf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484475-20191005.htm</a>"},{"pid":"af54fe6b74b3118faf67d99f8719acbec8685d55","tid":1626651,"uid":20222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:19:15.000Z","msg":"係咪見到有差佬打路人可以救?"},{"pid":"47d489473009a982ed63bd41f61d2991cce33828","tid":1626651,"uid":166763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"開口埋口暴徒"},{"pid":"0a6590c95d6b2f2ade30a5a2cc62f320b4336a10","tid":1626651,"uid":263223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"暴佢老母徒"},{"pid":"088e24745b10756a176a0a70de067d939a6024ef","tid":1626651,"uid":63792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"如果差佬拎槍比人打我救佢做乜撚<img src